唔會比人睇<br />\n<br />\n條女樣衰 <br />\n就話佢心地好囉 <br />\n<br />\n條仔好柒 <br />\n就話佢細心囉 <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係咁"},{"pid":"bc255757270ff33bbb9d2c0afe087d7eca58eda4","tid":53613,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:43:51.000Z","msg":"世上有不同生存方式 <br />\n<br />\n曱甴一樣可以快樂生活 <br />\n<br />\n但係有時行街見到一pair曱甴想扑野唔用套 <br />\n<br />\n我就一定反對"},{"pid":"30e08104107cac9b2ac1b95f9e7d301c139a3319","tid":53613,"uid":36454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:45:06.000Z","msg":"屈Sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}